name: Ave_Six_Marina_Accent_Chair_with_Inner_Box_Spring_and_Solid_Wood_Legs
reviews: Bought this chair in a navy for a client (actually bought 2) and she loves them. They make a classic, cool statement in her office and as a side chair in her new dining room. Easy to assemble & I highly recommend
Lovely chair - made well & looks great!
